G1 Z69.1 F720 ; Move print head further up
M73 P90 R0

G4 ; short wait

M221 S100 ; reset flow
M900 K0 ; reset LA



M104 S0 ; turn off hotend
M140 S40 ; set bed target to 40C (controlled cooldown)

M106 S255 ; fan 100%

M190 S40 ; wait until bed reaches 40C

; --- Move bed forward (head to back) ---
